    "Name": "Patriot",
    "Details": "The Patriot is built around an Arrow IV Artillery System. Four tons of ammunition gives it some flexibility between standard artillery rounds and homing missiles. Target Acquisition Gear allows it to call in friendly support should an enemy get within range. The only conventional weapon on the design is a Heavy PPC.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Stable</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.09</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Lower, Right Lower</color>",
